{"parse":{"title":"Cabinet Secretary for Government Business and Constitutional Relations","pageid":51525925,"revid":848104469,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n\n</p>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"width:22em\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">Cabinet Secretary for Government Business and Constitutional Relations</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;padding-bottom:0.4em; border-bottom:solid 1px #ccd2d9;\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/File:Scottish_Government_Logo.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Scottish Government Logo.svg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/01/Scottish_Government_Logo.svg/250px-Scottish_Government_Logo.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"52\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/01/Scottish_Government_Logo.svg/375px-Scottish_Government_Logo.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/01/Scottish_Government_Logo.svg/500px-Scottish_Government_Logo.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"512\" data-file-height=\"106\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<div style=\"padding-bottom:0.4em; border-bottom:solid 1px #ccd2d9; line-height:1.4em;\"><div style=\"padding-bottom:0.4em;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Michael_Russell,_Cabinet_Secretary_for_Education_%26_Lifelong_Learning_(2).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Michael Russell, Cabinet Secretary for Education &amp; Lifelong Learning (2).jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0d/Michael_Russell%2C_Cabinet_Secretary_for_Education_%26_Lifelong_Learning_%282%29.jpg/250px-Michael_Russell%2C_Cabinet_Secretary_for_Education_%26_Lifelong_Learning_%282%29.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"249\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0d/Michael_Russell%2C_Cabinet_Secretary_for_Education_%26_Lifelong_Learning_%282%29.jpg/375px-Michael_Russell%2C_Cabinet_Secretary_for_Education_%26_Lifelong_Learning_%282%29.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0d/Michael_Russell%2C_Cabinet_Secretary_for_Education_%26_Lifelong_Learning_%282%29.jpg/500px-Michael_Russell%2C_Cabinet_Secretary_for_Education_%26_Lifelong_Learning_%282%29.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"983\" data-file-height=\"981\" /></a></div><b>Incumbent<br /><a href=\"/wiki/Michael_Russell_(politician)\" title=\"Michael Russell (politician)\">Michael Russell</a> MSP</b><br />since&#160;June 2016</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Member of</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Scottish_Government\" title=\"Scottish Government\">Scottish Cabinet</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Appointer</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/First_Minister_of_Scotland\" title=\"First Minister of Scotland\">First Minister of Scotland</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Precursor</th><td>\nMinister for Justice</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Formation</th><td>\n2016</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Website</th><td>\n<span class=\"url\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.gov.scot\">www<wbr />.gov<wbr />.scot</a></span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Cabinet Secretary for Government Business and Constitutional Relations</b> is a <a href=\"/wiki/Scottish_cabinet\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Scottish cabinet\">cabinet position</a> in the <a href=\"/wiki/Scottish_Government\" title=\"Scottish Government\">Scottish Government</a>, replacing the Minister for UK Negotiations on Scotland's Place in Europe post.  The post was created in August 2016 during the <a href=\"/wiki/5th_Scottish_Parliament\" title=\"5th Scottish Parliament\">5th Scottish Parliament</a>. <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Responsibilities\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Responsibilities</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Supporting_Minister\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Supporting Minister</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#List_of_office_holders\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">List of office holders</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Minister_for_UK_Negotiations_on_Scotland&#39;s_Place_in_Europe\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Minister for UK Negotiations on Scotland's Place in Europe</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Responsibilities\">Responsibilities</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Cabinet_Secretary_for_Government_Business_and_Constitutional_Relations&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Responsibilities\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>The UK's exit from the European Union</li>\n<li>Government and parliamentary business</li>\n<li>Constitutional Relations and intra-governmental affairs</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Supporting_Minister\">Supporting Minister</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Cabinet_Secretary_for_Government_Business_and_Constitutional_Relations&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Supporting Minister\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Graeme_Dey\" title=\"Graeme Dey\">Graeme Dey MSP</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Minister_for_Parliamentary_Business_and_Veterans\" title=\"Minister for Parliamentary Business and Veterans\">Minister for Parliamentary Business and Veterans</a>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Cabinet_Secretary_for_Government_Business_and_Constitutional_Relations&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/wiki/United_Kingdom_European_Union_membership_referendum,_2016\" title=\"United Kingdom European Union membership referendum, 2016\">United Kingdom European Union membership referendum</a> took place on 23 June 2016. The following position was that Scottish government would be involved in the development of the UK government's position before the trigging of Article 50.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"List_of_office_holders\">List of office holders</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Cabinet_Secretary_for_Government_Business_and_Constitutional_Relations&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: List of office holders\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The current Cabinet Secretary for Government Business and Constitutional Relations is <a href=\"/wiki/Michael_Russell_(politician)\" title=\"Michael Russell (politician)\">Mike Russell</a> MSP.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" cellpadding=\"6\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0 0 0 1em; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaaaaa solid; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td colspan=\"7\">\n<h3><span id=\"Minister_for_UK_Negotiations_on_Scotland.27s_Place_in_Europe\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Minister_for_UK_Negotiations_on_Scotland's_Place_in_Europe\">Minister for UK Negotiations on Scotland's Place in Europe</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Cabinet_Secretary_for_Government_Business_and_Constitutional_Relations&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Minister for UK Negotiations on Scotland&#039;s Place in Europe\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Name\n</th>\n<th width=\"75\">Portrait\n</th>\n<th>Entered office\n</th>\n<th>Left office\n</th>\n<th>Party\n</th>\n<th>First Minister\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td bgcolor=\"#FEF987\">\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Michael_Russell_(politician)\" title=\"Michael Russell (politician)\">Mike Russell</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:Michael_Russell,_Cabinet_Secretary_for_Education_%26_Lifelong_Learning_(2).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Michael Russell, Cabinet Secretary for Education &amp; Lifelong Learning (2).jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0d/Michael_Russell%2C_Cabinet_Secretary_for_Education_%26_Lifelong_Learning_%282%29.jpg/75px-Michael_Russell%2C_Cabinet_Secretary_for_Education_%26_Lifelong_Learning_%282%29.jpg\" width=\"75\" height=\"75\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0d/Michael_Russell%2C_Cabinet_Secretary_for_Education_%26_Lifelong_Learning_%282%29.jpg/113px-Michael_Russell%2C_Cabinet_Secretary_for_Education_%26_Lifelong_Learning_%282%29.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0d/Michael_Russell%2C_Cabinet_Secretary_for_Education_%26_Lifelong_Learning_%282%29.jpg/150px-Michael_Russell%2C_Cabinet_Secretary_for_Education_%26_Lifelong_Learning_%282%29.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"983\" data-file-height=\"981\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td>26 August 2016\n</td>\n<td><i>incumbent</i>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Scottish_National_Party\" title=\"Scottish National Party\">Scottish National Party</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Nicola_Sturgeon\" title=\"Nicola Sturgeon\">Nicola Sturgeon</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Cabinet_Secretary_for_Government_Business_and_Constitutional_Relations&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Scottish_Parliament\" title=\"Scottish Parliament\">Scottish Parliament</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Scottish_Government\" title=\"Scottish Government\">Scottish Government</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Secretary_of_State_for_Exiting_the_European_Union\" title=\"Secretary of State for Exiting the European Union\">Secretary of State for Exiting the European Union</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Cabinet_Secretary_for_Government_Business_and_Constitutional_Relations&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref